data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 2011 Hillcroft Dr, nestled in the serene neighborhood of Highfield Park in Forest Hill.  Over 4,000 sq ft of living space.  This meticulously maintained property offers an exquisite blend of modern upgrades and timeless charm, making it the perfect sanctuary for discerning homeowners.Inside, on the upper level, you'll be greeted by the warmth of gleaming hardwood floors that flow throughout the main level, enhancing the home's inviting atmosphere. The focal point of the spacious great room is a stunning fireplace, where you can cozy up on chilly evenings and create lasting memories with loved ones. Prepare to be dazzled by the gourmet kitchen, a true masterpiece added in 2023, boasting sleek cabinetry, luxurious countertops, and top-of-the-line appliances. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or simply love to entertain, this culinary haven is sure to inspire your inner chef.  Indulge in the ultimate relaxation experience in the owner's bathroom, featuring a luxurious walk in shower w/duel body shower heads, that promises to rejuvenate your senses after a long day. With its spa-like ambiance, this private oasis is the perfect place to unwind and recharge.  Added bonus is the master bedroom also includes a  walk in closet.The lower level offers a fourth bedroom, and a half bath for additional living space. Also featured in the basement is a new floor added in 2023, offering endless possibilities for customization to suit your lifestyle needs.   Tax ID 1304033698 parcel of land .41 sold with sale of home.  Both parcels together total .88 acres of land.  Well pump 20'.  Hot water heater 22'.  HVAC systems is dual zoned.    Outside, the home showcases brand new siding installed in 2024, ensuring both durability and curb appeal that will impress at first sight. The partially wooded backyard offers a tranquil retreat, providing ample space for outdoor gatherings and leisurely afternoons spent in the fresh air.  For added convenience and peace of mind, this home features a new hot water heater installed in 2022 and a well pump updated in 2020, ensuring reliable performance for years to come.   With its perfect blend of modern amenities and timeless elegance,  don't miss your chance to make this exquisite property, zoned with Fallston schools, your forever home. Schedule your showing today and prepare to be captivated by all that this exceptional residence has to offer.
